replies.body:
I have a few questions!

1. In regards to Healing/**Self-Healing characters v. Grievous Wound-Effects**, if/when you decide to tackle them and/or remove Grievous Wounds, would you try to do them all at once or one at a time? What's your opinion on how this system should be designed?
{{champion:50}} {{champion:36}} 

2. In regards to **Stealth Characters v. Magical Sight**, if/when you decide to tackle them, would you try to do them all at once or one at a time? What's your opinion on how this system should be designed?
{{champion:29}} {{champion:17}} {{champion:84}} {{champion:107}} 

3. Developers have talked about **Ranged/Melee**, **High-Mobility/Low-Mobility** and **Manaless/Mana-Champions** and how there aren't *always *clear tradeoffs, as of now. Do you personally believe there will be "go-to" tradeoffs for being **Ranged**, **High-Mobility **or **Manaless**, or will that always be a case-by-case decision? What's your opinion on what those tradeoffs should be and accomplish?
{{champion:236}} {{champion:64}} {{champion:85}} {{champion:55}} 

(Icons are just examples, not a comment on the specific champions.)
